メソッドの詳細

getContributorId

long getContributorId()
The unique ID for the Analysis which provided the source data
for this ContributorFact.

戻り値:
the contributorID

getAnalysisId

long getAnalysisId()
The ID for the person who contributed the code measured in this
ContributorFact. The contributor_id is not globally unique.
It is derived from the author name found in the source control
server log, and is unique within the scope of an individual project only.

戻り値:
the analysisID

getContributorName

String getContributorName()
The name used by the author of this code when committing
to the source control server.

戻り値:
the contributorName

getAccountId

long getAccountId()
If this contribution has been claimed by an Ohloh member,
the element contains the unique ID of the Ohloh Account.
Otherwise, this element is omitted

戻り値:
the accountID.

getPrimaryLanguageId

int getPrimaryLanguageId()
The unique ID of the Language most often used by this contributor,
measured by the number of code lines added. If this contributor
has not committed any code in a language which Ohloh can recognize,
this value will be null.

戻り値:
the primaryLanguageID

getPrimaryLanguageNiceName

String getPrimaryLanguageNiceName()
The nice_name of the Language specified by primary_language_id.

戻り値:
the primaryLanguageNiceName

getCommentRatio

float getCommentRatio()
The fraction of new lines added by this contributor
which are comments. Note that Ohloh does not track
the net lines of current code attributable to an specific individual.
This statistic merely sums over all new lines added,
and does not consider whether the added lines were later removed
by this contributor or any other.

戻り値:
the commentRatio

getFirstCommitTime

Date getFirstCommitTime()
The time of the first commit by this contributor.

戻り値:
the firstCommitTime

getLastCommitTime

Date getLastCommitTime()
The time of the last commit by this contributor.

戻り値:
the lastCommitTime

getManMonths

int getManMonths()
The total number of calendar months in which this contributor
made at least one commit. Note that this is not simply the number
of months between first_commit_time and last_commit_time: months
in which there was no activity for this contributor are not counted.

戻り値:
the manMonths

getCommits

int getCommits()
The total number of commits made by this contributor.

戻り値:
the commits

getMedianCommits

int getMedianCommits()
Considering only months in which this contributor made at least one commit,
this is the median number of commits in a single month by this contributor.

戻り値:
the medianCommits

getContributorLanguageFact

List<ContributorLanguageFact> getContributorLanguageFact()
A collection of ContributorLanguageFacts may be included here,
covering statistics in individual Languages.
This collection is only present when ContributorFacts are queried individually.

戻り値:
the list of contributorLanguageFact
